{"id": "art-160", "label": "Art. 160", "title": "Art. 160", "slug": "art-160", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 160 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1557030427\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2012\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1557030427\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Situa&#355;iile</span> financiare ale\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> supuse <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iei</span>\nlegale de auditare vor fi auditate de c&#259;tre auditori financiari - persoane\nfizice sau persoane juridice -, în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_802127551\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2011\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_802127551\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>1</sup>)<span class=SpellE>Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> care opteaz&#259;, în temeiul art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>153</span><span style='color:black'>, pentru sistemul\ndualist de administrare sunt supuse auditului financiar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_439867322\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2010\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_439867322\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>2</sup>)<span class=SpellE>Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> ale c&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ii</span>\nfinanciare sunt supuse auditului financiar, potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legii</i> sau <span class=SpellE>op&#355;iunii</span>, în acest sens, a\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> pot s&#259; nu aplice prevederile\nart. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>159 alin. (1)</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, hot&#259;rârea în acest sens fiind luat&#259; de adunarea\ngeneral&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_270887978\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2009\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_270887978\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> ale\nc&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ii</span> financiare anuale sunt\nsupuse auditului financiar, potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>\nsau hot&#259;rârii <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, vor organiza\nauditul intern potrivit normelor elaborate de Camera Auditorilor Financiari din\nRomânia.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_646333487\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2008\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_646333487\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)La <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> ale\nc&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ii</span> financiare anuale nu sunt\nsupuse, potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, auditului\nfinanciar, adunarea general&#259; ordinar&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nva hot&#259;rî contractarea auditului financiar sau numirea cenzorilor,\ndup&#259; caz.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}